        Below is the URL for the drug indexes XML API

        %USERNAME% will be replaced with the users username
        %PASSWORD% will be replaced with the users password
    -->
    <string name="index_url" formatted="false">
        <![CDATA[http://www.injguide.nhs.uk/IMGDrugIndex.asp?username=%USERNAME%&password=%PASSWORD%]]>
    </string>
    <!-- This is the name of the XML tag which represents the start of a new drug index -->
